def calculate_max_chess_games(N: int) -> int:
    """
    Calculate the maximum number of complete chess games Chef can play in N hours.

    Args:
        N (int): The number of hours Chef has for playing chess.

    Returns:
        int: The maximum number of complete chess games Chef can play.
    """
    return N * 60 / 20
